<%= content_for :title, "Event example" %>

<div class="mx-auto md:w-2/3 w-full pt-4 flex flex-col">
  <div class="p-4 w-full my-4 bg-slgray border-gray-500 text-sblack flex flex-col">
    <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg inline-block">This is an Event example.
    <br>
    Start creating your own.</h3>
    <%= link_to "Get Started", 
      new_user_path, 
      data: { turbo_action: "replace" }, 
      class: "max-w-fit rounded-lg py-3 px-5 bg-sdred text-white font-medium mb-2" %>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-2 turbo-native:ml-2">
    <h3 class="mb-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-sdred">
      Novak Djokovic x Rafael Nadal
    </h3>

    <h4 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-800">
      Roland Garros
    </h4>

    <h5 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-800">
      05-10-2024 - 02:30
    </h5>

    <p class="mb-3 font-normal text-gray-700">
      <span class="bg-sdred text-white text-sm font-medium me-2 px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded">
        Tennis
      </span>
      <span class="bg-gray-500 text-white text-sm font-medium me-2 px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded">
        Start Plus
      </span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <p class="my-5 text-lg">
    Get ready for an epic showdown at Roland Garros between tennis 
    titans Novak Djokovic and Rafael Nadal. This match promises to 
    be a tournament highlight, showcasing the intense rivalry and 
    technical mastery of both players. As Djokovic aims for another 
    title, Nadal, the "King of Clay," seeks to defend his turf. 
    This game is more than a match; it's a historic battle that will 
    be etched in the annals of tennis.
  </p>

  <p class="mt-2">
    <div class="rounded-lg pt-3 pb-4 px-4 bg-sdred text-white flex font-medium">
      <%= inline_svg_tag("icons/watch.svg", style: "max-height: 30px; max-width: 30px; color: white") %>
      <span class="ml-2 pt-[5px]">Link to the streaming</span>
    </div>
  </p>
</div>
